title: Week 9 NFL Recap: Saints dominate Bucs, Steelers survive, Josh Allen back in MVP race? (Football 11/9)
description:
As they do every Sunday, the Pick Six Superfriends link up late at night to recap all the action in the NFL. Will Brinson, Ryan Wilson and John Breech cover everything you need to know from Week 9 including the Saints absolutely embarrassing Tom Brady and the Bucs on SNF, Tua Tagovailoa leading the Dolphins to another victory, the Steelers surviving a scare vs the Cowboys, Josh Allen outplaying Russell Wilson and much more.
Saints-Bucs (2:00)
Bills-Seahawks (15:00)
Dolphins-Cardinals (26:00)
Ravens-Colts (36:15)
Chiefs-Panthers (44:15)
Steelers-Cowboys (52:00)
Giants-Washington (57:00)
Titans-Bears (1:03:45)
Vikings-Lions (1:09:00)
Raiders-Chargers (1:13:30)
Texans-Jaguars (1:18:30)
Falcons-Broncos (1:23:45)
Winners/Losers (1:26:45)
